description: This stunning city loft style condo features breathtaking, expansive views of Back Bay, Downtown, and Boston Harbor! This thoughtfully designed one-bedroom, one-bathroom residence is located in the highly desirable, LEED Gold-certified Macallen Building. The living/dining area seamlessly connects to a newly renovated, modern kitchen. The spacious bedroom offers generous closet space and great views. The large ensuite bathroom includes a glass-enclosed tub/shower and ample counter space with custom built in storage cabinets. The grand hallway leading into your living room is equipped with custom built closets for maximum storage! This amenity-rich building features a vast roof deck with an in-ground heated pool, fitness center, media room, bike storage, and 24-hour concierge service. Ideally situated in South Boston, this location provides easy access to the South End, Seaport, public transportation, and highways. One garage parking space is included with this property.
